      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S is a purist\u2019s mid-engine configuration, powered by a 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six. The drivetrain features a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle delivering power to the rear wheels through an optional limited-slip differential. Mechanically robust, the engine benefits from a dry-sump lubrication system and exhibits excellent compression across all cylinders. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), offering variable damping rates for precise lateral stability and cornering poise. Braking performance is sharp, utilizing four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors. This example maintains its structural rigidity and communicative steering feel, with a suspension geometry that remains tight and responsive. A mechanically sound, high-performance machine ready for the enthusiast driver.",
