      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for 2018 BMW 540i xDrive, finished in a stunning Mediterranean Blue Metallic over a supple Cognac Dakota leather interior. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between executive luxury and athletic performance. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, with only minor, age-appropriate stone chips on the front fascia that do not detract from its presence. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the leather seats have been regularly conditioned and show no signs of cracking or heavy wear. Every technological feature, from the intuitive iDrive infotainment system to the Harman Kardon surround sound, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this 540i is in excellent health. The 3.0L turbocharged inline-six engine provides smooth, effortless power, and the xDrive all-wheel-drive system ensures confidence in all weather conditions. It has been serviced exclusively at certified centers, with a recent oil service and a fresh set of Pirelli Cinturato P7 tires installed just 4,000 miles ago. The brakes are firm, the suspension is quiet, and there are no warning lights on the dash. This is a non-smoker vehicle with a clean title, ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
